          <div class=\"left-menu\">\n                    <div class=\"head\">\n\n\n\n师资情况</div>\n                   <ul>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/lyys1.htm\" title=\"两院院士\"><li class=\"    \">两院院士</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/jsdw1.htm\" title=\"教师队伍\"><li class=\"   on   \">教师队伍</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/gcjsryjzy1.htm\" title=\"工程技术人员及职员\"><li class=\"    \">工程技术人员及职员</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/txry.htm\" title=\"退休人员\"><li class=\"    \">退休人员</li></a>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;height:25px;\"></div>\n</ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"right-main-box-box\">\n                    <div class=\"right-main-box\">\n                        <div style=\"width:100%;height:43px;\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"right-main\">\n                            <div class=\"right-map\">\n                                <div class=\"left\">\n\n\n\n教师队伍</div>\n                                <div class=\"right\">当前位置：\n                      <a href=\"../../index.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  首页</a>\n                &gt;\n              <a href=\"../../szqk/lyys1.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n              <a href=\"../../szqk/jsdw1.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  教师队伍</a>\n                &gt;\n                正文\n</div>\n                                </div>\n                             \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div class=\"szdw-detail right-column-box\">\n<div class=\"basic-box\">\n                                    <div class=\"timg\"><img src=\"/__local/0/F2/69/FDCEE1A48EE76DBBAAD1F45761E_D9150AE5_EBAE.png?e=.png\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"tbasic\">\n                                        <div class=\"tname\">易   迪</div>\n                                        <div class=\"tname-bg\"></div>\n                                        <div class=\"tag\">副教授</div>\n                                        <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                        <div class=\"tcontent\" style=\"height: 180px;\">\n                                            <p> \n\n     博士生导师<br>\n     \n     电话：010-62772851<br>\n\n      电子邮箱：<a href=\"mailto:diyi@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn\">diyi@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</a><br>\n     \n     办公地址：清华大学逸夫技术科学楼B811-1房间<br>\n\n\n\n</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                       <div class=\"more\" style=\"display: block;\"><span>展开更多&gt;&gt;</span></div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                </div>\n<ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">\n                                    <li title=\"title1\" class=\"on\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">教育背景</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title2\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">工作履历</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title3\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">学术兼职</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title4\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">研究领域</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title5\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">研究概况</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title6\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">奖励与荣誉</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title7\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">学术成果</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n \n                                    \n                                </ul>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title1 tli-content-on\">\n                                <div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2010/08-2015/07 加州大学伯克利分校，材料科学与工程系，博士，导师：Prof. Ramamoorthy Ramesh</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2006/08-2010/07 清华大学，材料科学与工程系，学士</p>\n</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title2 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2022/12-今 清华大学，材料学院，副教授</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2019/12-2022/11 清华大学，材料学院，助理教授</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2015/08-2019/11 斯坦福大学，应用物理系，博士后，合作导师：Prof. Yuri Suzuki</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title3 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">CPL、CPB、《物理学报》、《物理》四刊青年编委（2024–至今）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">中国材料进展期刊青年编委（2020–至今）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">中国材料研究学会材料分析表征分会理事（2023–至今）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">中国材料研究学会青年工作委员会理事（2022–至今）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">担任Adv. Mater., Phys. Rev. Lett., Nature Comm., Nature Nanotech. 等多个专业杂志审稿人</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title4 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\">为发展超低功耗信息存储器件提供新的材料解决方案，主要研究领域包括：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\">1.多铁性材料及异质结、磁电耦合效应及原型器件</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\">2.磁性绝缘体中的磁振子输运及调控</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\">3.氧化物自旋电子材料</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title5 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">课题组长期聚焦铁性量子材料及器件开展实验研究，深入探讨了具备铁电、铁磁及多铁性等具有广泛应用前景的材料及原型器件。通过高质量材料的可控制备、物理机制的深入探索以及原型器件的开发，在本领域取得了一系列得到国内外同行认可的科研成果，推动了多铁性量子材料及器件的发展。以第一/通讯作者身份在Nat. Comm., Phys. Rev. Lett., Adv. Mater., PNAS等材料和物理类核心期刊发表论文20余篇，在Science、Nature Materials、Nature Nanotech.等国际一流期刊共发表论文60余篇, 文章总引用近4000次，并多次受邀撰写本领域综述文章。主持基金委原创探索项目、重大研究计划培养项目、科技部重点研发计划课题等。获中国材料研究学会科学技术奖（基础研究类）一等奖、中国建材联合会/硅酸盐学会科学技术奖（基础研究类）一等奖、美国物理学会博士后奖等。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">课题组拥有激光分子束外延薄膜制备、高真空磁控溅射、综合物性测量系统、扫描探针显微镜、磁光克尔显微镜等实验设备，与合作团队在高频测试、器件制备等方面建立密切合作。每年招收1-2名博士生，长期欢迎博士后加入，也欢迎对信息功能材料有兴趣的本科生联系。</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title6 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2024年 中国材料研究学会科学技术奖（基础研究类）一等奖（排名第1）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2022年 中国建材联合会/硅酸盐学会科学技术奖（基础研究类）一等奖（排名第4）</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2019年 国家海外高层次人才青年项目</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">2019年 美国物理学会博士后奖 (Post-doctoral Award, APS March Meeting 2019)</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title7 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">部分代表性成果如下：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">1. H. Chen, D. Jiang, Y. Zhang, X. Qiu, Y. Liang, Q. Zhang, F. Zhu, T. Ohkochi, M. Chen, Y. Wang, J. Liu, Q. He, J. Ma, P. Yu, Y-H Lin, TX Nan*, <b>Di Yi*</b>, Pure spin current polarizer enabled by antiferromagnetic insulator, <b><i>Nature Communications</i></b> 16, 6257 (2025)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">2. H. Chen, X. Qiu, Z. Jin, D. Jiang, T. Lin, Y. Zhang, Y. Liang, X. Jiang, Y. Yang, C. Li, F. Zhu, J. Ma, Q. Zhang, J-C Lin, Q. He, Y-H Lin, TX Nan*, <b>Di Yi*</b>, Controlling Antiferromagnetic Magnon Transport and Anisotropy by Interfacial Coupling, <b><i>Advanced Functional Materials</i> </b>35, e07757 (2025)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">3. <b>Di Yi*</b>, CW Nan*, When relaxor films go ultrathin, <b><i>Nature Nanotechnology </i></b>20, 464 (2025)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">4. Y. Chai, Y. Liang, C. Xiao, Y. Wang, B. Li, D. Jiang, P. Pal, Y.n Tang, H. Chen, Y. Zhang, W. Skowroński6, Q. Zhang, L. Gu, J. Ma, P. Yu, J. Tang, Y-H Lin*,<b> Di Yi</b>*, D. C. Ralph, C-B Eom, H. Wu, TX Nan*, Voltage control of multiferroic magnon torque for reconfigurable logic-in-memory, <b><i>Nature Communications </i></b>15, 5975 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">5. A Tang, C. Li, T Xu, Y Dong, J. Ma, P Yu, CW Nan, Y-H Lin, TX Nan*, W. Jiang*, <b>Di Yi*</b>, Electric-Field Control of Perpendicularly Magnetized Ferrimagnetic Order and Giant Magnetoresistance in Multiferroic Heterostructures, <b><i>Nano Letters </i></b>24, 632 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">6. YH Liang, DS Jiang, YH Chai, Y Wang, HT Chen, J Ma, P Yu,<b> Di Yi</b>*, TX Nan*, Observation of Magnon Spin Transport in BiFeO3 Thin Films, <b><i>Advanced Functional Materials</i> </b>34, 2308944 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">7. HT Chen, DS Jiang, QH Zhang, YH Liang, JC Liu, AH Tang, YH Chai, P Yu, TX Nan,<b> Di Yi</b>*, Tuning Stoichiometry for Enhanced Spin-Charge Interconversion in Transition Metal Oxides, <b><i>Advanced Electronic Materials</i> </b>10, 202300666 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">8. <b>Di Yi</b>*, AH Tang, MM Kane, LB Xu, JC Liu, ZY Cheng, C Klewe, AT N'Diaye, P Shafer, P Yu, R Yu, HX Xu, YH Lin, CW Nan, Y Suzuki, Enhanced Ferromagnetism in Atomically Thin Oxides Achieved by Interfacial Reconstruction, <b><i>Advanced Functional Materials</i> </b>34, 202313294 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">9. D. Jiang, H. Chen, G. Ji, Y. Chai, C. Zhang, Y. Liang, J. Liu, W. Skowroński, P. Yu, <b>Di Yi*</b>, TX Nan*, Substrate-induced spin-torque-like signal in spin-torque ferromagnetic resonance measurement, <b><i>Physical Review Applied</i></b> 21, 024021 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">10. X. Qiu, Z. Wang, H. Chen, Y. Liang, X. Jiang, Y. Zhang, J. Ma, F. Zhu, TX Nan, Z. Chen, <b>Di Yi *</b>, Enhanced Exchange Bias in All-oxide Heterostructures with Cation-ordered Ferrimagnetic Double-perovskite, <b><i>npj Spintronics</i></b>, 2(1): 44 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">11. Y. Yang#, L. Zhao#, <b>Di Yi</b>#, T. Xu, Y. Chai, C. Zhang&amp;, D. Jiang&amp;, Y. Ji&amp;, D. Hou, W. Jiang*, J. Tang, P. Yu, H. Wu, TX Nan*, Acoustic-driven magnetic skyrmion motion, <b><i>Nature Communications 15</i></b> 1018 (2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">12. Y. Liang#, <b>Di Yi#</b>, TX Nan#, L. Zhao, S. Liu, Y. Zhang, H. Chen, T. Xu, J-M Hu, J. Shi, W. Jiang*, R. Yu*, Y-H Lin*, “Field-free spin-orbit switching of perpendicular magnetization enabled by dislocation-induced in-plane symmetry breaking”, <b><i>Nature Communications </i></b>14, 5458 (2023)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">13. A. Tang, T. Xu, S. Liu, Y. Liang, H. Chen, D. Yan, Y. Shi, P. Yu, R. Yu, Y. Lin, T. Nan, W. Jiang*, <b>Di Yi*,</b> “Implementing Complex Oxides for Efficient Room-Temperature Spin-Orbit Torque Switching”, <b>Advanced Electronic Materials</b>, 8, 11, 202201245 (2022)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">14. H. Chen, <b>Di Yi*</b>, Spin-charge conversion in transition metal oxides, <b>APL Materials</b> 9, 060908 (2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">15. <b>Di Yi</b>*, H. Amari, P. P. Balakrishnan, C. Klewe, A. T. N'Diaye, P. Shafer, N. Browning, Y. Suzuki, Interface-Driven Perpendicular Magnetic Anisotropy by Symmetry Control in Oxide Superlattices, <b>Physical Review Applied</b> 15, 024001 (2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">16. <b>Di Yi*</b>, Y. Wang, O. M. J. van’t Erve, L. Xu, H. Yuan, M. Veit, P. Balakrishnan, Y. Choi, A. T. N’Diaye, P. Shafer, E. Arenholz, H. Xu*, P. Yu*, B. T. Jonker and Y. Suzuki. “Emergent electrical control of phase transformation in oxide superlattices”, <b>Nature Communications</b>, 11(1): 902 (2020)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;\">（完整论文列表可见于<span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Google Scholar</span>）</p>\n                                </div>\n \n</div>  \n\n</form>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:100px;\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    \n   <div class=\"footer-box\">\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:40px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"links\">\n                <div class=\"title\">常用链接</div>\n               <ul>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1690762525, 69199)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/journal-of-materiomics/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1690762525, 69201)\"><li>Journal of Materiomics</li></a>\n</ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"contact\"><script language=\